
Usage:
  php morphine COMMAND [--help]

Commands:
  config            - Set or get configuration options for morphine [ alt: con    ]
  generate          - Generates packages, modules, workflows, etc   [ alt: gen    ]
  execute           - Executes a workflow in a package              [ alt: exe    ]
  install           - Installs a package or module                  [ alt: ins    ]
  update            - Checks the package server for updates         [ alt: upd    ]
  test              - Runs the test suite for a package             [ alt:        ]
  help              - Displays this help file                       [ alt: --help ]

See 'php morphine COMMAND --help'
